node.text: This month on #PrimarkSpotlight, we meet the incredibly talented singer/songwriter @iamkyami. Kyami chats to us about finding empowerment within her true sound and pushing through failures to find successes. On a chilled Friday vibe? Make sure you go and check out 'IAmKyami' on Spotfiy for the ultimate soundtrack to match your mood ✨ #Primark #FeelGoodFriday
